        In this sample, you can select and highlight any point in the chart by clicking on or touching it. Additionally, you have the option to select and highlight a point during the initial loading of the chart using the <code>SelectedDataIndexes</code> option.
    </p>
    <p>
        <code>Tooltip</code> is enabled in this example. To see the tooltip in action, hover over a point or tap on a point on touch-enabled devices.
    </p>
}
